  "remarks": "JSC Iliadis is a company based in Russia. It was established as a subsidiary of LLC Titul, a company based in Russia owned by Dimitry Aleksandrovich Beloglazov, and it acquired Oleg Deripaska’s share in the International LLC Rasperia Trading Limited (“Rasperia”, based in Russia). Rasperia owns 28,5 million shares in the European company STRABAG SE. Those shares were frozen because Rasperia was controlled by Oleg Deripaska, an individual subject to Union restrictive measures.",
